   Carroll, Andrew; Sundquist, Andreas; Daly, Richard; Duyk, Geoff, DNAnexus, Mountain View, CA 94040 USA.
   Yu, Fuli; Gibbs, Richard A., Baylor Coll Med, Dept Mol \& Human Genet, Houston, TX 77030 USA.
   Boerwinkle, Eric, Univ Texas Hlth Sci Ctr Houston, Ctr Human Genet, Houston, TX 77030 USA.},
