   Qiu, Xingting, Gannan Med Univ, Dept Radiol, Affiliated Hosp 1, Ganzhou, Peoples R China.
   Tan, Wenjun, Key Lab Intelligent Comp Med Image, Minist Educ, Shenyang, Peoples R China.
   Liao, Liefa, Jiangxi Univ Sci \& Technol, Sch Informat Engn, Ganzhou, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.3389/fonc.2022.773840},
