   CAPILLARY-ELECTROPHORESIS; 6-AMINOQUINOLYL-N-HYDROXYSUCCINIMIDYL
   CARBAMATE; CHEMICAL DERIVATIZATION; FLUORESCENCE DETECTION; COLUMN
