   Katz, Lee S., Ctr Res Dis Prevent, Atlanta, GA 30333 USA.
   Beiko, Robert G., Dalhousie Univ, Halifax, NS B3H 4R2, Canada.
   Hsiao, William, BC Publ Hlth Microbiol \& Reference Lab, Vancouver, BC V5Z 4R4, Canada.
   Brinkman, Fiona, Simon Fraser Univ, Burnaby, BC V5A 1S6, Canada.},
