   Dey, Damini; Germano, Guido; Slomka, Piotr J.; Berman, Daniel S., Univ Calif Los Angeles, David Geffen Sch Med, Dept Med, Los Angeles, CA 90095 USA.
   Wong, Nathan D., Univ Calif Irvine, Dept Med, Heart Dis Prevent Program, Irvine, CA 92717 USA.
   Kakadiaris, Ioannis, Univ Houston, Dept Comp Sci, Houston, TX 77204 USA.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.atherosclerosis.2009.08.032},
Keywords = {Pericardial fat; Thoracic fat; Non-contrast CT; Coronary calcium;
