   Verhelst, Pieter-Jan; Meewis, Jeroen; Vandemeulebroucke, Arne; Shaheen, Eman; Politis, Constantinus; Jacobs, Reinhilde, Katholieke Univ Leuven, Dept Imaging \& Pathol, Fac Med, OMFS IMPATH Res Grp, Kapucijnenvoer 33, BE-3000 Leuven, Belgium.
   Smolders, Andreas; Beznik, Thomas; Van Gerven, Adriaan; Willems, Holger, Relu BV, Kapeldreef 60, BE-3001 Leuven, Belgium.
   Jacobs, Reinhilde, Karolinska Inst, Dept Dent Med, Box 4064, S-14104 Huddinge, Sweden.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.jdent.2021.103786},
EarlyAccessDate = {NOV 2021},
