   Wolfe, Alan J., Loyola Univ Chicago, Div Hlth Sci, Stritch Sch Med, Dept Microbiol \& Immunol, Maywood, IL 60153 USA.
   Hunter, Christie L., SCIEX Ltd, Redwood City, CA 94065 USA.
   Gibson, Bradford W., Univ Calif San Francisco, Dept Pharmaceut Chem, San Francisco, CA 94143 USA.},
DOI = {10.1021/acs.analchem.5b02983},
Keywords-Plus = {LOW-ABUNDANCE PROTEINS; QUANTITATIVE ASSESSMENT; HISTONE MODIFICATIONS;
