   Klein, Travis J., Queensland Univ Technol, Inst Hlth \& Biomed Innovat, Brisbane, Qld, Australia.
   Zenobi-Wong, Marcy, Swiss Fed Inst Technol, Cartilage Engn Regenerat, Zurich, Switzerland.
   Gawlitta, Debby, Univ Med Ctr Utrecht, Dept Oral \& Maxillofacial Surg \& Special Dental C, Utrecht, Netherlands.
   Malda, Jos, Univ Utrecht, Dept Equine Sci, Fac Vet Med, Utrecht, Netherlands.},
