   Langs, Georg; Peloschek, Philipp; Bischof, Horst; Kainberger, Franz, Med Univ Vienna, Dept Radiol, Computat Image Anal \& Radiol CIR Lab, A-1090 Vienna, Austria.
   Peloschek, Philipp; Kainberger, Franz, Med Univ Vienna, Ctr Diag Res \& Therapy Musculoskeletal Disorders, Dept Radiol, Ctr Bone \& Joint, A-1090 Vienna, Austria.
