   Ist Zooprofilatt Sperimentale Umbria Marche, I-06126 Perugia, Italy.
   Univ Greenwich, Sch Chem \& Life Sci, Chatham ME4 4TB, Kent, England.
   Univ Urbino, Ist Sci Tossicol Igienist \& Ambientali, I-61029 Urbino, Italy.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.fm.2003.10.008},
Keywords = {Listeria monocytogenes; hlyA; paramagnetic nanoparticles; milk},
Keywords-Plus = {POLYMERASE-CHAIN-REACTION; ESCHERICHIA-COLI; REACTION ASSAY; FOOD;
