   Dell'Aquila, Maria Elena, Univ Bari Aldo Moro, Dept Biosci Biotechnol \& Biopharmaceut, Km3 Str Casamassima, I-70100 Bari, Italy.
   Ramalho-Santos, Joao, Univ Coimbra, CNC Ctr Neurosci \& Cell Biol, Biol Reprod \& Stem Cell Grp, Rua Larga, P-3004504 Coimbra, Portugal.
