   pharmaceuticals; Process monitoring; Vertical farming unit},
Keywords-Plus = {TRANSIENT PROTEIN EXPRESSION; NUTRIENT FILM TECHNIQUE; LARGE-SCALE
   PRODUCTION; MONOCLONAL-ANTIBODY; NICOTIANA-TABACUM; MYCOTOXIN
   CONTAMINATION; TECHNOECONOMIC ANALYSIS; IRRIGATION FREQUENCY; INFLUENZA
   VACCINE; ANIMAL FEED},
