   O'Grady, Justin; Mwaba, Peter; Kapata, Nathan; Bates, Matthew; Zumla, Alimuddin, Univ Coll London Med Sch UNZA UCLMS, Res \& Training Programme, Univ Teaching Hosp, Lusaka, Zambia.
   Maeurer, Markus, Karolinska Inst, Dept Microbiol Tumour \& Cell Biol, Stockholm, Sweden.
   Mwaba, Peter; Kapata, Nathan, Minist Hlth, Lusaka, Zambia.
   Hoelscher, Michael, Klinikum Univ Munich, Dept Infect Dis \& Trop Med, Munich, Germany.},
