   Calle, A., CNM CSIC, Inst Microelect Madrid, Madrid, Spain.
   Rodriguez-Frade, J. M.; Mellado, M., CSIC, Ctr Nacl Biotecnol, Dept Inmunol \& Oncol, Madrid, Spain.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.talanta.2009.01.012},
Keywords = {SPR; Immunosensor; Self-assembled monolayer; hGH; Point-of-care device;
