   281/292), while reorientation was successful in 97.2\% of the studies
   (166/171 + 216/222 + 273/281). No significant difference in success
   rates for (TI)-T-201 versus Tc-99m-sestamibi images was found.
   Conclusion: Our automated approach to myocardial perfusion SPECT
