   Levy, Simon; Cohen-Adad, Julien, Univ Montreal, Funct Neuroimaging Unit, Montreal, PQ, Canada.
   Schneider, Torben, Philips Healthcare, Guildford, Surrey, England.
   Smith, Alex K.; Smith, Seth A., Vanderbilt Univ, Inst Imaging Sci VUIIS, 221 Kirkland Hall, Nashville, TN 37235 USA.
   Smith, Alex K.; Smith, Seth A., Vanderbilt Univ, Dept Biomed Engn, Nashville, TN 37235 USA.
