   Barbosa, Daniel; Heyde, Brecht; D'hooge, Jan, Katholieke Univ Leuven, Lab Cardiovasc Imaging \& Dynam, Louvain, Belgium.
   Barbosa, Daniel; Dietenbeck, Thomas; Friboulet, Denis; Bernard, Olivier, Univ Lyon 1, CNRS, INSERM, INSA Lyon,CREATIS,UMR5220,U630, F-69622 Villeurbanne, France.
   Houle, Helene, Siemens Ultrasound, Mountain View, CA USA.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.ultrasmedbio.2012.08.008},
Keywords = {Active contours; LV volume analysis; image segmentation; B-splines; 3-D
