   Chuntib, Prakit; Themsirimongkon, Suwaphid; Saipanya, Surin; Jakmunee, Jaroon, Chiang Mai Univ, Res Lab Analyt Instrument \& Electrochem Innovat, Fac Sci, Chiang Mai 50200, Thailand.
   Jakmunee, Jaroon, Chiang Mai Univ, Ctr Excellence Innovat Chem, Fac Sci, Chiang Mai 50200, Thailand.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.talanta.2017.03.073},
Keywords = {Screen-printed carbon electrode (SPCE); Carbon nanotubes (CNTs); Nafion;
   Sequential injection analysis; Differential pulse voltammetry; Paraquat},
Keywords-Plus = {SQUARE-WAVE VOLTAMMETRY; PASTE ELECTRODE; LIQUID-CHROMATOGRAPHY;
