   Nebbak, A.; Bitam, I., USTHB, Fac Biol Sci, Lab Biodivers \& Environm Interact Genomes, Bab Ezzouar, Algeria.
   Almeras, L., Inst Rech Biomed Armees, Dept Malad Infect, Unite Parasitol \& Entomol, Marseille, France.},
DOI = {10.1111/mve.12250},
Keywords = {Ctenocephalides felis felis; Rhipicephalus sanguineus; Innovative
   strategy; MALDI-TOF MS; Protocol standardized},
Keywords-Plus = {FLIGHT MASS-SPECTROMETRY; DESORPTION IONIZATION-TIME;
