   Avram, Robert; Olgin, Jeffrey E.; Barrios, Joshua; Abreau, Sean; Soni, Krishan; Tison, Geoffrey H., Univ Calif San Francisco, Dept Med, Div Cardiol, Cardiol, 505 Parnassus Ave, San Francisco, CA 94143 USA.
   Avram, Robert; Tardif, Jean-Claude, Univ Montreal, Montreal Heart Inst, Dept Med, Div Cardiol, 5000 Rue Belanger, Montreal, PQ H1T 1C8, Canada.
